# Implementation Plan: MERN Manufacturer Showcase, Configurator & Lead Platform

Build a premium, production-ready MERN Stack application for **TimeWell Mattress Factory**, preserving the existing design language (deep navy and gold accents, clean spacious typography, floating WhatsApp, and interactive configurators) while adding dynamic backend administration, lead tracking, and SEO utilities.

