## Proposed Changes

### Database Schemas

#### 1. `Product` Model
Stores mattress and sofa metadata.
- `name` (String, required)
- `slug` (String, unique, required)
- `category` (String: `'mattress'` or `'sofa'`)
- `description` (String)
- `shortDescription` (String)
- `basePrice` (Number, default base rate)
- `retailMultiplier` (Number, default: `2.0` - used to display comparison showroom price)
- `images` ([String], Cloudinary URLs)
- `isAvailable` (Boolean, default: `true`)
- `isFeatured` (Boolean, default: `false`)
- `specifications` (Map of Strings, e.g., Warranty, Firmness)
- `benefits` ([String])
- `ratings` (Number, default: `4.8`)
- `reviewsCount` (Number, default: `50`)
- `mattressCoreType` (String: `'ortho' | 'latex' | 'spring' | 'dual' | 'coir'`, optional)
- `sofaCategory` (String: `'l-shape' | 'recliner' | '2-seater' | '3-seater' | 'corner' | 'custom'`, optional)

#### 2. `MattressConfig` Model
Dynamic options and pricing multipliers for mattresses.
- `cores`: `[{ type: String, name: String, basePrice: Number, desc: String, layers: [{ name: String, height: String, color: String }] }]`
- `sizes`: `[{ name: String, multiplier: Number }]`
- `thicknesses`: `[{ name: String, multiplier: Number }]`

#### 3. `SofaConfig` Model
Dynamic options and pricing multipliers for sofas.
- `sofaTypes`: `[{ name: String, multiplier: Number }]`
- `materials`: `[{ name: String, priceModifier: Number }]`
- `fabrics`: `[{ name: String, priceModifier: Number }]`
- `colors`: `[{ name: String, colorCode: String }]`
- `seatingCapacities`: `[{ capacity: Number, multiplier: Number }]`

#### 4. `Lead` Model
Captures client details and custom configuration details.
- `name` (String, required)
- `phone` (String, required)
- `email` (String, required)
- `productName` (String, required)
- `category` (String, required)
- `configuration` (Object, stores size, thickness, material, etc.)
- `quotedPrice` (Number, required)
- `message` (String)
- `status` (String, default: `'pending'`)
- `createdAt` (Date, default: `Date.now`)

#### 5. `Testimonial` Model
- `name` (String)
- `avatar` (String)
- `rating` (Number)
- `dateText` (String, e.g., "2 weeks ago")
- `text` (String)

#### 6. `HomepageContent` Model
- `heroTitle` (String)
- `heroSubtitle` (String)
- `heroSubheading` (String)
- `ctaTitle` (String)
- `ctaSubtitle` (String)

