### Backend API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|--------|----------|--------|-------------|
| **POST** | `/api/auth/login` | Public | Authenticate admin, returns JWT |
| **PUT** | `/api/auth/update` | Admin | Change admin credentials |
| **GET** | `/api/products` | Public | Fetch all products (with query filter) |
| **GET** | `/api/products/:slug` | Public | Fetch single product by slug |
| **POST** | `/api/products` | Admin | Create new product (with Cloudinary uploads) |
| **PUT** | `/api/products/:id` | Admin | Edit existing product details |
| **DELETE**| `/api/products/:id` | Admin | Delete product |
| **GET** | `/api/configs/mattress`| Public | Fetch mattress configuration and pricing multipliers |
| **PUT** | `/api/configs/mattress`| Admin | Update mattress configuration rules |
| **GET** | `/api/configs/sofa` | Public | Fetch sofa configuration rules |
| **PUT** | `/api/configs/sofa` | Admin | Update sofa configuration rules |
| **POST** | `/api/leads` | Public | Create a new lead |
| **GET** | `/api/leads` | Admin | Fetch and search leads list |
| **DELETE**| `/api/leads/:id` | Admin | Delete lead record |
| **GET/POST/PUT/DELETE** | `/api/testimonials` | Mixed | Testimonial CRUD |
| **GET/PUT** | `/api/homepage` | Mixed | Hero, banners, and featured config |
| **GET** | `/sitemap.xml` | Public | Dynamically generated sitemap of all routes & products |

