### Dynamic Pricing Algorithms

#### Mattress Pricing
$$\text{Quoted Price} = \text{Base Price} \times \text{Size Multiplier} \times \text{Thickness Multiplier}$$
$$\text{Showroom Price} = \text{Quoted Price} \times \text{Retail Multiplier}$$

#### Sofa Pricing
$$\text{Quoted Price} = (\text{Base Price} \times \text{Type Multiplier} \times \text{Seating Multiplier}) + \text{Material Modifier} + \text{Fabric Modifier}$$
$$\text{Showroom Price} = \text{Quoted Price} \times \text{Retail Multiplier}$$

