### SEO Configuration & Local Business Markup

We will design a custom SEO engine in React using a `<MetaTags>` component that updates:
- `<title>`
- Meta Description & Keywords
- Open Graph tags (`og:title`, `og:description`, `og:image`, `og:url`)
- JSON-LD Structured Data for Products and Local Business.

#### Product Structured Data Example:
```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org/",
  "@type": "Product",
  "name": "Ortho-Memory Foam Mattress",
  "image": "https://cloudinary.com/ortho.png",
  "description": "High spine support mattress",
  "offers": {
    "@type": "Offer",
    "priceCurrency": "INR",
    "price": "6500",
    "availability": "https://schema.org/InStock",
    "seller": {
      "@type": "LocalBusiness",
      "name": "TimeWell Mattress Factory"
    }
  }
}
```

